{"tid":129732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文明中国]中國客蹂躪無印良品","createTime":"2017-02-21T22:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T10:25:25.000Z","uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9522b5efe66a14b73855a17e56a0308bcb0abd8f","tid":129732,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:05:14.000Z","msg":"在宜家淪陷之後，無印良品（MUJI）也無法「保持清白」了！近日有內地媒體踢爆，日式百貨無印良品的中國分店，也難逃被內地消費者的不文明舉動蹂躪，呼籲大家不要成為國民素質的反面教材，也請尊重其他顧客的感受。<br />\n印象中的日本百貨無印良品是整齊、乾淨、劃一的格局。然而，看看現實中的內地MUJI店舖，服裝區裏顧客比試後隨意亂扔的衣服亂七八糟；化妝品區，被弄得七倒八歪的唇彩、被顧客隨意丟棄在別的貨架上的化妝棉，有些顧客在挑選護膚產品時，當發現有的沒有試用裝，竟還擅自打開一件全新的商品！最慘不忍睹的是文具櫃枱，明明有試筆紙不用，隨意在待售的簿子封面塗塗畫畫，還有把憤青之情帶去逛MUJI的，寫下：「還我釣魚島！」<br />\nMUJI裏的家居區，像宜家一樣，成為了蹭睡霸坐的重災區，更有情侶光天化日眾目睽睽之下大被同眠。儘管店裏貼着明確的告示「請勿坐卧休息」，依然阻攔不了這些脫鞋上床的行為，不僅有礙雅致，有時還有臭氣。除了種種不文明現象，甚至還有小偷小盜的犯罪事件頻頻發生。有在MUJI兼職的朋友爆料說，只剩包裝而裏面商品不翼而飛的情況很常見，更有些人把試用裝塞進包裝盒，而把裏面原來的商品順手牽羊。<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170222/19935959?_ga=1.205092371.2073979554.1479480943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19935959%3F_ga%3D1.205092371.2073979554.1479480943&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=556754f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19935959%3F_ga%3D1.205092371.2073979554.1479480943&h=851ce827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170222/19935959?_ga=1.205092371.2073979554.1479480943</a>"},{"pid":"3eb5fc4b68d617ed0783c6d7e8c537bec37907fd","tid":129732,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:07:38.000Z","msg":"中國人天性低賤, 希望快d滅種, 日資公司快d撤資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29526fe6ed869e1d3eec74dc64261d8aaf022ba","tid":129732,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:08:12.000Z","msg":"中國人就買翻明創鳩撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b4c85dd0ba9293ef01e727c563290e93c1cee8","tid":129732,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3170827adb3971269992f4018f68667066a4a102","tid":129732,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:28:14.000Z","msg":"邊個叫你去支那開分店"},{"pid":"90555c1f6778cb78e156f9048ebc291bec750d50","tid":129732,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"muji人工低工又西，係時候反抗"},{"pid":"927c58a023cff8747ef843fdad126cfa38413f0e","tid":129732,"uid":6590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:33:45.000Z","msg":"你會期望狗唔會周街柯屎柯尿<br />\n唔會鐘意就踎底？"},{"pid":"71931b9438962a742559a834dd476aed9ebfc752","tid":129732,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:49:01.000Z","msg":"竟然唔屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d976dc3af61bd3f8e8098ed786f9583ef2c2964d","tid":129732,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然唔屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該頒個進步獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9484fd95c8415e6355b3a611d9bb6e8aa0b189f3","tid":129732,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然唔屙屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無報唔代表無屙"},{"pid":"28b020fba955d7de50e0fc66df0a939aa49484a0","tid":129732,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:16:19.000Z","msg":"放啲釘喺床玉裡面，一瞓落去就爽啦"},{"pid":"865c2e1aff053a9346354c59e3d99f040378776c","tid":129732,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:24:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放啲釘喺床玉裡面，一瞓落去就爽啦</blockquote><br />\n裝airbag先係,一坐上去就自動彈出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e93c07f9c83df69c424795473ee44965878ca1","tid":129732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37c531b3959d7d7615d31a26337f1f9784e32f1","tid":129732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170222/19935959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19935959&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=40263a39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19935959&h=fe1f2bb3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170222/19935959</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170222/large/22ce5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170222%2Flarge%2F22ce5p.jpg&h=50c432b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在宜家淪陷之後，無印良品（MUJI）也無法「保持清白」了！近日有內地媒體踢爆，日式百貨無印良品的中國分店，也難逃被內地消費者的不文明舉動蹂躪，呼籲大家不要成為國民素質的反面教材，也請尊重其他顧客的感受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170221/photo/bkncn-20170221210010168-0221_05011_001_02b.jpg?20170221223342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170221%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170221210010168-0221_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20170221223342&h=423a87c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170221/photo/bkncn-20170221210010168-0221_05011_001_04b.jpg?20170221223342\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170221%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170221210010168-0221_05011_001_04b.jpg%3F20170221223342&h=f207d592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印象中的日本百貨無印良品是整齊、乾淨、劃一的格局。然而，看看現實中的內地MUJI店舖，服裝區裏顧客比試後隨意亂扔的衣服亂七八糟；化妝品區，被弄得七倒八歪的唇彩、被顧客隨意丟棄在別的貨架上的化妝棉，有些顧客在挑選護膚產品時，當發現有的沒有試用裝，竟還擅自打開一件全新的商品！最慘不忍睹的是文具櫃&amp;#26545;，明明有試筆紙不用，隨意在待售的簿子封面塗塗畫畫，還有把憤青之情帶去逛MUJI的，寫下：「還我釣魚島！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170222/large/22ce7p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170222%2Flarge%2F22ce7p.jpg&h=7e321a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMUJI裏的家居區，像宜家一樣，成為了蹭睡霸坐的重災區，更有情侶光天化日眾目睽睽之下大被同眠。儘管店裏貼&amp;#30528;明確的告示「請勿坐&amp;#21351;休息」，依然阻攔不了這些脫鞋上床的行為，不僅有礙雅致，有時還有臭氣。除了種種不文明現象，甚至還有小偷小盜的犯罪事件頻頻發生。有在MUJI兼職的朋友爆料說，只剩包裝而裏面商品不翼而飛的情況很常見，更有些人把試用裝塞進包裝盒，而把裏面原來的商品順手牽羊。"},{"pid":"dd25a18edccd1694a70d20a56a05e4f846de1708","tid":129732,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"間公司忍到先係重點. 先唔講阻唔阻止. 為左一地區既市場.<br />\n比人影到呢D圖出去外國甚至國際. 影響晒成個品牌比人最重要既賣點同<br />\nSELLING POINT. 值得咩?"},{"pid":"b255d9f3b66a3afeca3d0930895a0b2aeec1b68a","tid":129732,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:51:32.000Z","msg":"華人生番賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ec6d9f0dbba7e9401a6c8c129935b229b92671","tid":129732,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:58:48.000Z","msg":"呢個程度都可以用文明高低黎分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b51587827250f17a1cc774eab0c1e1a93d24483","tid":129732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1303367b4b9a552a2383c7024bcbd75beaa54525","tid":129732,"uid":51302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"屌你開喺支那預左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e291609317dd5071b937002e0259971e25335ad","tid":129732,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>還有把憤青之情帶去逛MUJI的，寫下：「還我釣魚島！」</blockquote><br />\n又黎身體好撚誠實,反日但係又去行無印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b883dee6c5a541ace96fe065ad9fe9df936a419","tid":129732,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fcd9fd90be6f0ef986abd31edec41fe68dc4cd","tid":129732,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你唔爭氣係都要支那開店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0d87e86b40fd48a8f6d823947c2fb9b1e13b93","tid":129732,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"賺支那錢係咁㗎啦"},{"pid":"12918fe7e1602d7ba47f1033cb9581b2155474e0","tid":129732,"uid":29708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔係去名創優品<br />\n唔係山寨比正版更好咩"}]}